PERSISTENT MODES
	(F,F) IS NONDET
	(B,F) IS NONDET
	(F,B) IS NONDET
END
pasteSnippet("throws(?Callable,?ExType)", "Method or Constructor ?Callable is declared to throw exception of type ?ExType").


